    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206720/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1713970011\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206720/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1713970011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206720/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1713970011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206720/extras/70fe3a0f453427aa59d775dd0abf8b7a.poster.avif?t=1713970011\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206720/extras/70fe3a0f453427aa59d775dd0abf8b7a.webm?t=1713970011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206720/extras/70fe3a0f453427aa59d775dd0abf8b7a.mp4?t=1713970011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你扮演一名被派往特帕斯实验室调查一系列奇怪事件的检查员。这个实验室长期以来一直出现异常现象，你的任务就是找出真相。准备好迎接一场激动人心的冒险，这场冒险结合了2D像素艺术射击游戏的元素，快速的动作以及敌人的大军。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206720/extras/bc6d04677f0b2f8f3e0be5fcf70a4f25.poster.avif?t=1713970011\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206720/extras/bc6d04677f0b2f8f3e0be5fcf70a4f25.webm?t=1713970011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206720/extras/bc6d04677f0b2f8f3e0be5fcf70a4f25.mp4?t=1713970011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在 Lab Inspect 中，你将体验到动态的游戏玩法，面对敌人的人潮，使用各种武器突围而出。你手中有各种各样的火器，每种在不同的情况下都有效。敌人会一波一波地袭来，这需要你快速反应和战略思考。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206720/extras/9dd4d6ede1a7eafbeadc1b3c1d2df472.poster.avif?t=1713970011\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206720/extras/9dd4d6ede1a7eafbeadc1b3c1d2df472.webm?t=1713970011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206720/extras/9dd4d6ede1a7eafbeadc1b3c1d2df472.mp4?t=1713970011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>探索实验室的不同关卡，揭开其中的秘密，并与头目战斗，以进入新的区域。你走得越远，游戏的激烈程度越高，敌人也会变得更强、更多。音效设计和游戏风格营造出一种紧张而危险的氛围。<br><br><strong>游戏特色：</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>多种武器选择来对抗敌人。<br></li><li>敌人一波接一波地袭来。<br></li><li>强烈的硬核游戏玩法，考验你的技能。<br></li><li>独特美学的生动像素艺术图形。<br></li><li>充满谜团和意外转折的引人入胜的故事情节。</li></ul>",
